41:37','2018-12-12 17:41:37','','mighty oak','','inherit','open','closed','','%d1%84%d0%be%d0%bd-2','','','2018-12-12 18:41:45','2018-12-12 17:41:45','',51,'http://oakwoodtimber.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/фон.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(259,1,'2018-12-12 18:42:16','2018-12-12 17:42:16','And for that there are several reasons. From oak boards you get beautiful, durable and wear-resistant floors, each with its own character. Various methods of surface treatment and abrasion make it possible to achieve many infinite variations. But even after such manipulations, the individuality of the oak floor still manifests itself in the natural patterns of knots and wood fibers. It is difficult to remain indifferent to this majestic tree. So what is surprising is that we make so many genders from oak?\r\n\r\nThe Caucasus is a region of Russia, famous for its forests. Oaks grow here in abundance. And here, in the Caucasus, is our factory, on which the wood of these oaks is transformed into billets for the further production of parquet. Due to the territorial proximity, we can visit suppliers at any time to make sure that the forestry is conducted in accordance with the principles of sustainable development.','Mighty Oak','','inherit','closed','closed','','51-autosave-v1','','','2018-12-12 18:42:16','2018-12-12 17:42:16','',51,'http://oakwoodtimber.com/51-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(263,1,'2018-12-13 08:27:12','2018-12-13 07:27:12','','dubove_podlahy_llc','','inherit','open','closed','','dubove_podlahy_llc','','','2018-12-13 08:27:12','2018-12-13 07:27:12','',0,'http://oakwoodtimber.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/dubove_podlahy_llc.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(265,1,'2018-12-13 08:56:02','2018-12-13 07:56:02','','cooperation solid oak flooring manufacturer','','inherit','open','closed','','cooperation-solid-oak-flooring-manufacturer','','','2018-12-13 08:56:02','2018-12-13 07:56:02','',0,'http://oakwoodtimber.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/cooperation-so